snippet.title: Fallen Worlds Trailer 2
snippet.description: Fallen worlds is a unique mix of action-RPG, hack 'n' slash, roguelite and roguelike elements, with a heavy emphasis on looting. It brings dungeon crawling to a new level with the best elements of your favorite RPG's and fantastic stylized graphics!
